entry.def: A washer is a thin flat ring of metal or rubber which is placed over a bolt before the nut is screwed on.
A washer is the same as a washing machine .

means.word_mean: 1. someone who washes things for a living
2. seal consisting of a flat disk placed to prevent leakage
3. a home appliance for washing clothes and linens automatically
